                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18281023-190-victim992 t18281023-190-viclabel1111"></join>, and live at the <placeName id="t18281023-190-crimeloc1112">Red Lion public-house, in Cockspur-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18281023-190-crimeloc1112" type="placeName" value="Red Lion public-house, in Cockspur-street"></interp>
