            . I am a pawnbroker. The prisoner pawned this watch with me on the 3d of October.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. When the prosecutor came to me at Bayswater, he said if I would give him his watch he did not want to have any more trouble about it.</p>
